title: Episode 65 - Jessimae Peluso
itunes:title: Episode 65 - Jessimae Peluso
description: I'm joined by an Italian American angel, comedian and host of The Sharp Tongue Podcast, Jessimae Peluso. We talk comedy and all things Italian food and family. And look for her new show, Tattoo Redo, on Netflix.
